<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    </head>
    <body style="background-color: #f2f2f2; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif">
        <main style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem; background-color: #ffffff">
            <div style="border-bottom: 2px solid #1a1a1a; padding-bottom: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem">
                <h1 style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: #1a1a1a; margin: 0">Thank you for your message!</h1>
            </div>

            <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: #1a202c; line-height: 1.6">
                Hello {{name}},<br /><br />
                Thank you for reaching out. I have received your message and will get back to you as soon as possible.<br /><br />
                Here is a summary of your inquiry:
            </p>

            <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #1a202c; margin: 1rem 0">
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 0.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: 600; width: 140px; vertical-align: top">Name</td>
                    <td style="padding: 0.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb">{{name}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 0.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: 600; vertical-align: top">Email</td>
                    <td style="padding: 0.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb">{{email}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 0.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: 600; vertical-align: top">Company</td>
                    <td style="padding: 0.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb">{{company}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 0.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: 600; vertical-align: top">Project Type</td>
                    <td style="padding: 0.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb">{{projectType}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 0.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: 600; vertical-align: top">Budget</td>
                    <td style="padding: 0.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb">{{budget}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 0.5rem 0; font-weight: 600; vertical-align: top">Message</td>
                    <td style="padding: 0.5rem 0">{{{messageHtml}}}</td>
                </tr>
            </table>

            <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: #1a202c; line-height: 1.6">
                Best regards,<br />
                Robert Julian Kratz
            </p>

            <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem; padding-top: 1rem; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #9ca3af">
                <p style="margin: 0">
                    This message was sent to <strong>{{email}}</strong>. If you did not send a message, you can safely ignore this email.
                </p>
            </div>
        </main>
    </body>
</html>
